<Author>alissa024
<Content>Modern hotel, great for business or tourists We stayed at this hotel at the expense of another NH hotel (Duc la Victoria) over booking. So we were lucky in the fact that our daily rate didn't change. This 4-star hotel is very sleek/modern, clean and comfortable. Not to mention its great shower and beds! The hotel is only a 10 min walk from Placa Catalunya and not even a 5 min walk to the closest metro (Uranquioa). We found taxis to be rather cheap so all in all location wasn't even an issue.There isn't much excitement going on around the hotel, i.e. restaurants or shopping, but it is well worth the stay for the luxury of the room (esp when luxury isn't a well-known commodity in Europe)I would recommend this hotel to anyone who can afford it! 
