<Author>TravellingGypsy
<Content>Loved It This was my first trip to Barcelona and the NH Podium helped make it wonderful. We stayed there for 3 days. Our breakfast was included in the price and it was typical European with pastries, small sandwiches, cheeses, hams, yogurt, champagne, water, OJ, and milk. The staff was friendly and courteous. My Toyota 4Runner wouldn't fit in their garage, so they found a garage where it would fit. They provided with maps and pointed out all the sites that were close by and even recommended their city's best beaches. I would stay again the future as the hotel was wonderful and situated close to the Sagrada Familia, La Perdrera, and the Arc de Triomf. 
